        "description": {
          "value": "<p>While any simulacrum exists, divinations aimed at the <em>real</em> Ileosa silently target a simulacrum instead (@Check[type:arcana|dc:40] as the spell is cast to notice — not where it went). This also catches <em>dream</em>-, <em>nightmare</em>-, and <em>sending</em>-type spells, but not telepathy.</p>"
