        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A blood-simulacrum: half the queen's memories, none of her power; at 0 HP she goes rigid and <strong>melts into a pool of blood</strong> (@Check[type:arcana|dc:27] to read a variant simulacrum; full answers only at the Everdawn Pool). Seated on the Crimson Throne: +10 AC and immunity to illusions and mental effects.</p>"
        },
